{"tid":1865892,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說黃絲，試著說變革者","createTime":"2020-02-06T12:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T05:44:53.000Z","uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa0b689de533fab811b818eb3c86b27d8bd05b6","tid":1865892,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"真普選是為了與美國即將來到的對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be903c2b0ba2ba8c0023e4a6b59a3665e9f48954","tid":1865892,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:23:57.000Z","msg":"堅離地城：沈旭暉國際生活台 Simon's Glos World<br />\n<br />\n在美國大學任教的朋友，關於黃藍、左右在香港的定義有以下觀察：<br />\n<br />\n「如果保守主義(在英美政壇的傳統定義)，是指捍衛一種自由公民社會的傳統生活方式，那麼香港的黃營，才是真正的保守派。好像章怡和筆下的那種『最後的貴族』，真正的高貴氣質，在大陸找不到。<br />\n<br />\n香港的藍營，特別是深藍，其實是激進左/右派，他們是激進派，因為他們要改變香港人自1841年以來的生活方式和社會習慣。<br />\n<br />\n用中史的角度看：香港的深藍/紅，其實就是商鞅，就是李斯，就是法家。而黃營呢，就是先秦貴族社會，文化多元。大陸就是贏秦，香港就是先秦。香港的反送中風暴，其實是中華文明二千幾百年來，兩條政治文化路線之爭。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/posts/2988147637886033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%2Fposts%2F2988147637886033&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAskVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=93960947\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/posts/2988147637886033</a>"},{"pid":"deffe0d7ca530e973e038f8fff7b8b67ac9d6155","tid":1865892,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"a jump to the sky turns to a rider kick"},{"pid":"7401a1a63a787b1340bdf6bfc30d7a5ed05b9d3c","tid":1865892,"uid":85180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:43:47.000Z","msg":"高達都冇部，學咩人叫變革者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd90e4a48ca5e7cf92f1b38952790a9617ecf71","tid":1865892,"uid":8410,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:49:36.000Z","msg":"不如叫攘夷志士"},{"pid":"a659d73a1bff3e8d68